<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-39-0957 </DOCNO><TEXT>Based on several investigations of gas works, the fundamentals for anobjective risk assessment of former gas work locations are presented.As an essential marginal parameter here, the future utilization of thesite is included in the evaluation. The aim is, on the one hand to helpthe owners of former gas works sites in their decision, on the otherhand to demonstrate which marginal parameters should be considered whenassessing the risks of former gas work sites.</TEXT></DOC>